5
00:01:23,960 --> 00:01:25,220
You really went all out

6
00:01:25,400 --> 00:01:26,280
for your uncle.

7
00:01:26,480 --> 00:01:27,440
Don't worry.

8
00:01:27,640 --> 00:01:29,240
If you get cyber violence one day,

9
00:01:29,240 --> 00:01:30,770
I'll back you up right away.

10
00:01:31,240 --> 00:01:32,500
Come on, don't jinx me.

11
00:01:33,759 --> 00:01:34,080
Hey,

12
00:01:34,400 --> 00:01:36,080
you look quite cool in the video.

13
00:01:36,080 --> 00:01:36,680
Let me see.

14
00:01:37,710 --> 00:01:39,650
[Han Miao]

15
00:01:39,720 --> 00:01:41,490
