♪ Yet waking brings only
a boundless white haze ♪

22
00:02:08,930 --> 00:02:11,270
♪ How many summers has life ever known ♪

23
00:02:11,760 --> 00:02:14,880
♪ Only in winter nights do I realize ♪

24
00:02:39,800 --> 00:02:40,360
Miao.

25
00:02:40,880 --> 00:02:41,280
What?

26
00:02:41,840 --> 00:02:43,079
I need to tell you something.

27
00:02:43,079 --> 00:02:43,610
Go ahead.

28
00:02:45,960 --> 00:02:46,720
I feel

29
00:02:48,200 --> 00:02:51,000
something's wrong with my heart lately.

30
00:02:52,160 --> 00:02:52,720
What?

31
00:02:53,200 --> 00:02:54,460
You can't ignore that.

32
00:02:54,720 --> 00:02:55,520
I'll go to the hospital with you.

33
00:02:55,520 --> 00:02:56,440
Wait, wait.

34
00:02:58,040 --> 00:03:00,240
Maybe I'll just keep an eye on it for now.

35
00:03:02,520 --> 00:03:03,320
Alright then,

36
00:03:04,360 --> 00:03:05,720
I'll hang up now.

37
00:03:05,800 --> 00:03:06,320
Okay.

38
00:03:07,120 --> 00:03:07,600
Bye.

39
00:03:16,360 --> 00:03:17,760
Jiang Jun told the police

40
00:03:18,280 --> 00:03:20,210
we said the event budget was tight,

41
00:03:20,440 --> 00:03:22,700
hinting he could buy cheap ingredients.

42
00:03:23,240 --> 00:03:24,640
That backstabbing jerk.

43
00:03:25,200 --> 00:03:26,400
What a load of lies.

44
00:03:26,960 --> 00:03:27,600
Jiang Jun?

45
00:03:30,800 --> 00:03:31,660
I remember now.

46
00:03:32,220 --> 00:03:33,329
[Gu Group]

47
00:03:33,329 --> 00:03:37,150
[Children-Friendly Community's
Parent-Child Park Open Day]

48
00:03:37,450 --> 00:03:38,480
[Mini Community]

49
00:03:38,480 --> 00:03:39,040
Lin Ze,

50
00:03:39,880 --> 00:03:42,160
the Parent-Child Day
starts this afternoon.

51
00:03:42,160 --> 00:03:43,360
Is everything ready?

52
00:03:43,840 --> 00:03:44,900
Don't worry, Boss,

53
00:03:44,960 --> 00:03:46,480
I checked three times this morning.

54
00:03:46,480 --> 00:03:48,079
There won't be any mistakes.

55
00:03:49,120 --> 00:03:50,050
Most important—

56
00:03:50,160 --> 00:03:51,880
make sure the kids' food is safe.

57
00:03:51,880 --> 00:03:53,079
No slip-ups.

58
00:03:56,640 --> 00:03:57,730
Forget it, I'll check it myself.

59
00:03:57,730 --> 00:03:59,350
[Children-Friendly Community's
Parent-Child Park Open Day]

60
00:04:06,400 --> 00:04:07,330
Here, take this.

61
00:04:08,200 --> 00:04:08,760
Make sure

62
00:04:09,520 --> 00:04:10,580
this is done right.

63
00:04:15,600 --> 00:04:16,240
Jiang Jun.

64
00:04:19,680 --> 00:04:21,040
Are all the ingredients ready?

65
00:04:21,040 --> 00:04:22,560
Mr. Gu wants to check them himself.

66
00:04:22,560 --> 00:04:23,000
Okay.

67
00:04:23,120 --> 00:04:23,760
All set.

68
00:04:24,040 --> 00:04:25,440
Mr. Gu, this way, please.

69
00:04:28,080 --> 00:04:29,480
The man meeting Jiang Jun

70
00:04:29,480 --> 00:04:30,800
is definitely suspicious.

71
00:04:30,800 --> 00:04:31,440
So what's

72
00:04:31,680 --> 00:04:32,600
our next move?

73
00:04:33,159 --> 00:04:34,960
He Wei hitting me now

74
00:04:35,640 --> 00:04:36,970
can't be a coincidence.

75
00:04:37,600 --> 00:04:38,200
Here's the plan—

76
00:04:38,200 --> 00:04:39,120
you go after Jiang Jun,

77
00:04:39,120 --> 00:04:40,250
I'll go after He Wei.

78
00:04:40,440 --> 00:04:40,840
Okay.

79
00:04:58,000 --> 00:04:58,560
Make sure

80
00:04:59,280 --> 00:05:00,340
this is done right.

81
00:05:31,760 --> 00:05:33,760
You've already taken all the money.

82
00:05:33,840 --> 00:05:35,800
What else do you want?

83
00:06:14,960 --> 00:06:16,160
Who was that just now?

84
00:06:16,680 --> 00:06:18,040
What… who?

85
00:06:18,160 --> 00:06:20,360
I don't know what you're talking about.

86
00:06:31,840 --> 00:06:32,280
He Wei.

87
00:06:34,400 --> 00:06:35,060
Who are you?

88
00:06:38,720 --> 00:06:40,180
It doesn't matter who I am.

89
00:06:41,680 --> 00:06:42,610
What matters is,

90
00:06:44,080 --> 00:06:45,880
I've got a business deal for you.

91
00:06:48,680 --> 00:06:50,080
I really don't know.

92
00:06:50,600 --> 00:06:52,240
He came to warn me.

93
00:06:52,840 --> 00:06:53,480
He told me not

94
00:06:53,480 --> 00:06:54,240
to say I was paid

95
00:06:54,240 --> 00:06:56,440
to slander you during that livestream.

96
00:06:57,320 --> 00:06:59,600
They didn't even give me the last payment,

97
00:06:59,600 --> 00:07:01,360
and still expect me to keep my mouth shut.

98
00:07:01,360 --> 00:07:02,600
What do you want?

99
00:07:03,240 --> 00:07:04,080
Stop!

100
00:07:04,360 --> 00:07:04,920
He Wei,

101
00:07:05,760 --> 00:07:06,920
you're so cautious.

102
00:07:07,480 --> 00:07:08,480
Even if he won't tell you,

103
00:07:08,480 --> 00:07:10,480
you'll still dig until you find out.

104
00:07:13,400 --> 00:07:14,400
If you won't talk,

105
00:07:14,760 --> 00:07:16,120
I'll go to the police.

106
00:07:17,040 --> 00:07:18,760
They'll know right away

107
00:07:19,080 --> 00:07:20,280
you're the leak.

108
00:07:21,320 --> 00:07:22,380
Trying to set me up?

109
00:07:23,400 --> 00:07:24,040
Don't you want to know

110
00:07:24,040 --> 00:07:25,700
where your mother Luo Qian is?

111
00:07:25,840 --> 00:07:27,000
If I want answers,

112
00:07:28,200 --> 00:07:30,320
I'll make you tell me sooner or later.

113
00:07:32,480 --> 00:07:33,880
Last chance—

114
00:07:35,280 --> 00:07:35,640
talk

115
00:07:36,520 --> 00:07:37,360
or not.

116
00:07:38,040 --> 00:07:38,840
Your choice.

117
00:07:40,960 --> 00:07:42,090
I'm out of patience.

118
00:07:46,240 --> 00:07:47,370
His name's Zhu Ming.

119
00:07:49,120 --> 00:07:49,600
He...

120
00:07:50,000 --> 00:07:51,400
works for Qin's Group.

121
00:08:04,040 --> 00:08:04,970
You little punk.

122
00:08:05,600 --> 00:08:06,200
You'll pay

123
00:08:07,120 --> 00:08:08,080
for what you did.

124
00:08:11,440 --> 00:08:12,800
Get in touch with Zhu Ming.

125
00:08:12,800 --> 00:08:13,680
Pay him off,

126
00:08:15,160 --> 00:08:16,960
and tell him not to come for work.

127
00:08:17,120 --> 00:08:19,040
The company's transferring him.

128
00:08:19,600 --> 00:08:20,860
Mr. Gu, you can't go in.

129
00:08:22,400 --> 00:08:23,000
Mr. Gu.

130
00:08:24,800 --> 00:08:25,400
Mr. Qin.

131
00:08:27,920 --> 00:08:28,780
Leave us alone.

132
00:08:29,080 --> 00:08:29,940
Go back to work.

133
00:08:30,240 --> 00:08:30,680
Yes.

134
00:08:36,280 --> 00:08:38,010
Mr. Gu, you came without a word.

135
00:08:38,440 --> 00:08:39,240
What's up?

136
00:08:42,320 --> 00:08:42,880
Qin Mian,

137
00:08:44,120 --> 00:08:45,240
risking children's lives

138
00:08:45,240 --> 00:08:47,000
over a piece of land—

139
00:08:48,640 --> 00:08:50,370
don't you think that's too far?

140
00:08:51,680 --> 00:08:52,240
Sorry,

141
00:08:52,880 --> 00:08:55,140
I have no idea what you're talking about.

142
00:09:01,400 --> 00:09:03,260
The kitchen may not have cameras,

143
00:09:03,400 --> 00:09:05,260
but there was a Gu's truck outside

144
00:09:05,720 --> 00:09:07,120
with a dash cam.

145
00:09:08,090 --> 00:09:09,540
[October 2024]

146
00:09:21,760 --> 00:09:23,760
I've sent the footage to the police.

147
00:09:24,480 --> 00:09:25,520
By now,

148
00:09:25,760 --> 00:09:26,960
your man Zhu Ming

149
00:09:27,600 --> 00:09:29,600
should've finished his statement.

150
00:09:34,640 --> 00:09:36,760
Zhu Ming may be my employee,

151
00:09:37,360 --> 00:09:39,720
but he's also a grown man.

152
00:09:40,320 --> 00:09:41,050
His actions

153
00:09:41,640 --> 00:09:43,160
don't represent Qin's Group,

154
00:09:43,160 --> 00:09:44,320
and certainly not me.

155
00:09:44,320 --> 00:09:46,520
Then explain it to the police yourself.

156
00:10:00,920 --> 00:10:01,440
Hello?

157
00:10:03,200 --> 00:10:04,120
Yes, I am.

158
00:10:06,320 --> 00:10:06,980
No problem.

159
00:10:07,400 --> 00:10:09,660
I'll cooperate with the investigation.

160
00:10:14,040 --> 00:10:15,040
Qin Mian, listen,

161
00:10:16,280 --> 00:10:18,040
about what you did to the children,

162
00:10:18,040 --> 00:10:19,640
I'll make you pay.

163
00:10:23,880 --> 00:10:26,880
So you're really willing
to be Gu Changfeng's lapdog?

164
00:10:28,360 --> 00:10:29,360
With your talent,

165
00:10:30,200 --> 00:10:32,000
it's a pity that you just hand him

166
00:10:32,120 --> 00:10:33,080
all the prize.

167
00:10:35,320 --> 00:10:35,760
Why not

168
00:10:36,160 --> 00:10:37,290
join forces with me?

169
00:10:37,920 --> 00:10:39,440
I'll help you take over Gu's Group.

170
00:10:39,440 --> 00:10:40,440
What do you think?

171
00:10:43,760 --> 00:10:45,560
Mr. Qin, mind your own business.

172
00:10:46,360 --> 00:10:47,800
Don't worry about me.

173
00:10:49,400 --> 00:10:51,640
Aren't you curious how I found

174
00:10:52,160 --> 00:10:53,360
He Wei so quickly?

175
00:11:05,520 --> 00:11:06,450
What do you mean?

176
00:11:08,400 --> 00:11:09,600
Don't you want to know

177
00:11:10,240 --> 00:11:12,320
why your birth mother abandoned you?

178
00:11:13,000 --> 00:11:14,880
Whose blood runs in your veins?

179
00:11:16,720 --> 00:11:17,780
You know my mother?

180
00:11:19,880 --> 00:11:20,280
Dad.

181
00:11:22,400 --> 00:11:23,130
Gu Jingyuan,

182
00:11:23,360 --> 00:11:24,080
please leave,

183
00:11:24,080 --> 00:11:25,340
or I'll call security.

184
00:11:27,200 --> 00:11:28,730
I've got other things to do,

185
00:11:28,840 --> 00:11:29,900
so I won't keep you.

186
00:11:30,280 --> 00:11:31,560
If you're interested,

187
00:11:32,280 --> 00:11:33,610
come have tea next time.

188
00:11:42,000 --> 00:11:42,360
Dad,

189
00:11:43,520 --> 00:11:44,560
is what he said true?

190
00:11:44,560 --> 00:11:45,960
Did you order Manager Zhu

191
00:11:46,040 --> 00:11:47,370
to mess with Gu's Group?

192
00:11:47,960 --> 00:11:49,760
Dad, why are you always picking on them?

193
00:11:49,760 --> 00:11:50,220
Shut up.

194
00:11:51,360 --> 00:11:52,760
This has nothing to do with you.

195
00:11:52,760 --> 00:11:54,090
Stop talking nonsense.

196
00:11:54,920 --> 00:11:55,650
Avoid coming

197
00:11:55,800 --> 00:11:57,260
to the company these days.

198
00:12:05,560 --> 00:12:06,820
He Wei's gone missing?

199
00:12:08,360 --> 00:12:09,360
Alright, I got it.

200
00:12:11,160 --> 00:12:13,020
Why are you still watching He Wei?

201
00:12:13,440 --> 00:12:15,720
You seem to have something
on your mind these days.

202
00:12:15,720 --> 00:12:16,960
Are you hiding something

203
00:12:16,960 --> 00:12:17,520
from me?

204
00:12:18,200 --> 00:12:18,760
No.

205
00:12:19,120 --> 00:12:21,520
I just don't want him
causing more trouble.

206
00:12:21,920 --> 00:12:22,240
Oh.

207
00:12:22,760 --> 00:12:23,360
By the way,

208
00:12:24,880 --> 00:12:26,160
take these flowers,

209
00:12:28,240 --> 00:12:29,300
and give them to Xi.

210
00:12:29,480 --> 00:12:30,480
She'll love them.

211
00:12:35,840 --> 00:12:36,680
Ms. Qiao Yan.

212
00:12:37,560 --> 00:12:38,080
Xi,

213
00:12:38,720 --> 00:12:40,120
you look lively today.

214
00:12:40,600 --> 00:12:42,280
Feeling better?

215
00:12:42,680 --> 00:12:43,480
Miss Qiao Yan,

216
00:12:43,680 --> 00:12:44,120
Mr. Gu,

217
00:12:45,080 --> 00:12:46,240
I misunderstood you before.

218
00:12:46,240 --> 00:12:47,040
I'm sorry.

219
00:12:47,120 --> 00:12:47,760
It's okay.

220
00:12:47,960 --> 00:12:48,960
We understand.

221
00:12:49,480 --> 00:12:51,280
As long as the kids are healthy,

222
00:12:51,440 --> 00:12:51,840
right?

223
00:12:52,080 --> 00:12:52,640
Mr. Gu,

224
00:12:53,080 --> 00:12:54,080
she loves the toy

225
00:12:54,320 --> 00:12:55,050
you gave her—

226
00:12:55,360 --> 00:12:56,890
sleeps with it every night.

227
00:12:59,160 --> 00:12:59,600
Xi,

228
00:13:00,680 --> 00:13:02,440
if you ever feel unwell again,

229
00:13:02,720 --> 00:13:03,720
you must tell me,

230
00:13:03,920 --> 00:13:04,440
okay?

231
00:13:08,320 --> 00:13:08,840
Xi,

232
00:13:09,000 --> 00:13:09,930
don't be afraid.

233
00:13:10,400 --> 00:13:11,160
He

234
00:13:11,280 --> 00:13:11,880
just looks

235
00:13:12,320 --> 00:13:13,440
a bit serious.

236
00:13:14,200 --> 00:13:15,000
But actually,

237
00:13:15,120 --> 00:13:15,980
he's very nice.

238
00:13:16,000 --> 00:13:17,260
See? Pretty, isn't it?

239
00:13:17,280 --> 00:13:18,680
He bought it just for you.

240
00:13:19,320 --> 00:13:19,720
Here.

241
00:13:26,880 --> 00:13:27,440
Yan,

242
00:13:27,840 --> 00:13:29,560
you're so nice to him.

243
00:13:29,840 --> 00:13:31,170
Are you his girlfriend?

244
00:13:31,520 --> 00:13:32,200
Hey,

245
00:13:32,920 --> 00:13:33,920
watch your mouth.

246
00:13:34,600 --> 00:13:35,120
Sorry,

247
00:13:35,480 --> 00:13:36,440
she's just a kid.

248
00:13:36,920 --> 00:13:37,520
It's okay.

249
00:13:41,840 --> 00:13:43,320
I'll go pack up for you.

250
00:13:43,800 --> 00:13:44,480
Great.

251
00:13:44,720 --> 00:13:45,450
Come with me.

252
00:13:47,600 --> 00:13:48,800
I'll go with you.

253
00:14:18,560 --> 00:14:20,290
My heart is beating hard again.

254
00:14:34,960 --> 00:14:35,760
What's wrong?

255
00:14:41,440 --> 00:14:43,570
Maybe I've just been too tired lately.

256
00:14:44,760 --> 00:14:46,690
Probably worrying over my issues.

257
00:14:47,800 --> 00:14:48,800
Get some rest

258
00:14:48,960 --> 00:14:50,160
and leave the rest to me.

259
00:14:50,160 --> 00:14:50,840
Find something

260
00:14:50,840 --> 00:14:52,240
you enjoy doing.

261
00:14:53,400 --> 00:14:53,880
Yan.

262
00:14:54,040 --> 00:14:54,720
Come on.

263
00:14:54,960 --> 00:14:55,880
Coming.

264
00:15:00,540 --> 00:15:00,880
[Qin Group]

265
00:15:00,880 --> 00:15:02,610
Do you think Qin's is behind it?

266
00:15:02,720 --> 00:15:04,160
It's hard to say.

267
00:15:04,280 --> 00:15:04,880
Yeah.

268
00:15:04,880 --> 00:15:05,480
What should we do?

269
00:15:05,480 --> 00:15:06,360
Don't forget what I told you.

270
00:15:06,360 --> 00:15:06,960
Hey, Mr. Qin.

271
00:15:06,960 --> 00:15:07,360
Okay.

272
00:15:07,440 --> 00:15:07,900
Mr. Qin,

273
00:15:08,040 --> 00:15:09,240
according to authorities,

274
00:15:09,240 --> 00:15:10,900
the food poisoning incident

275
00:15:10,960 --> 00:15:12,120
at Gu's Parent-Child Day event

276
00:15:12,120 --> 00:15:13,880
was caused by Qin's malicious competition.

277
00:15:13,880 --> 00:15:14,610
Is that true?

278
00:15:14,880 --> 00:15:15,540
Everyone,

279
00:15:15,880 --> 00:15:17,400
it has been investigated.

280
00:15:17,840 --> 00:15:19,840
Our marketing manager Zhu Ming

281
00:15:20,280 --> 00:15:21,280
used underhanded

282
00:15:21,440 --> 00:15:23,080
tactics for personal gain.

283
00:15:23,560 --> 00:15:24,480
He's been fired

284
00:15:25,280 --> 00:15:27,320
and will face legal action.

285
00:15:29,720 --> 00:15:31,560
The company is also a victim—

286
00:15:32,680 --> 00:15:34,520
but I feel deeply guilty

287
00:15:35,680 --> 00:15:37,480
and will compensate

288
00:15:38,040 --> 00:15:40,120
the children and parents.

289
00:15:41,440 --> 00:15:42,040
I'm sorry.

290
00:15:42,060 --> 00:15:44,550
[Qin Group]

291
00:15:48,280 --> 00:15:49,760
The scandal handed

292
00:15:50,200 --> 00:15:51,800
the disputed land

293
00:15:52,040 --> 00:15:53,760
to Gu's without a fight

294
00:15:54,200 --> 00:15:56,730
and shattered
Qin Real Estate's reputation,

295
00:15:56,920 --> 00:15:58,400
casting a shadow

296
00:15:58,680 --> 00:16:00,080
over its transition.

297
00:16:00,100 --> 00:16:02,800
