447
00:25:42,160 --> 00:25:42,480
Yes.

448
00:25:42,520 --> 00:25:43,120
Well...

449
00:25:43,320 --> 00:25:44,240
It's late. Let me give you a ride.

450
00:25:44,240 --> 00:25:44,680
No.

451
00:25:45,520 --> 00:25:45,960
I...

