466
00:26:33,520 --> 00:26:35,480
to transfer you money?

467
00:26:35,720 --> 00:26:37,840
He really think he's your elder.

468
00:26:40,680 --> 00:26:42,280
I don't know why—

469
00:26:43,200 --> 00:26:44,600
