477
00:26:59,680 --> 00:27:00,120
First,

478
00:27:00,480 --> 00:27:02,010
there's no blood relation.

479
00:27:02,160 --> 00:27:02,620
Second,

480
00:27:02,920 --> 00:27:04,450
he's only a few years older.

481
00:27:04,760 --> 00:27:06,480
Liking him doesn't make you a pervert.

482
00:27:06,480 --> 00:27:08,320
But we're family.

483
00:27:08,720 --> 00:27:10,560
