489
00:27:29,440 --> 00:27:30,120
Honestly,

490
00:27:30,800 --> 00:27:32,320
I haven't figured it out.

491
00:27:34,000 --> 00:27:35,080
Maybe I've been

492
00:27:35,080 --> 00:27:36,520
through a lot these days.

493
00:27:37,600 --> 00:27:39,640
I might have got confused

494
00:27:40,920 --> 00:27:41,400
and

495
00:27:41,880 --> 00:27:43,360
caused him trouble.

496
00:27:43,920 --> 00:27:44,840
You're sure

497
00:27:45,120 --> 00:27:46,320
it's just confusion?

498
00:27:53,280 --> 00:27:54,520
What matters now

499
00:27:56,120 --> 00:27:57,980
is finding my parents' murderer.

500
00:28:00,120 --> 00:28:01,760
