512
00:28:29,480 --> 00:28:30,210
I have to go.

513
00:28:30,520 --> 00:28:31,000
Okay.

514
00:28:31,840 --> 00:28:32,840
Yan, you're back.

515
00:28:36,720 --> 00:28:37,960
Morning, Uncle.

516
00:28:38,640 --> 00:28:39,170
Morning.

517
00:28:39,560 --> 00:28:40,360
Going to work?

518
00:28:40,920 --> 00:28:41,320
Yes.

519
00:28:42,200 --> 00:28:42,880
Well,

520
00:28:43,280 --> 00:28:44,480
you're back so early.

521
00:28:44,520 --> 00:28:46,380
Didn't stay longer with Han Miao?

522
00:28:47,320 --> 00:28:48,040
I'm done.

523
00:28:50,400 --> 00:28:52,460
I'll go back if there's nothing else.

524
00:28:54,800 --> 00:28:55,320
Yan.

525
00:29:00,880 --> 00:29:01,760
Come with me.

526
00:29:02,000 --> 00:29:03,460
I've got something to say.

527
00:29:33,160 --> 00:29:34,560
-Qiao Yan.
-Gu Jingyuan.

528
00:29:35,680 --> 00:29:37,340
How much older are you than me?

529
00:29:38,640 --> 00:29:39,200
Uh...

530
00:29:40,080 --> 00:29:41,210
F-Five years older.

531
00:29:41,480 --> 00:29:41,920
See?

532
00:29:42,840 --> 00:29:44,100
Only five years older—

533
00:29:44,200 --> 00:29:45,240
and I'm calling you Uncle?

534
00:29:45,240 --> 00:29:46,370
That's unfair to me.

535
00:29:46,920 --> 00:29:47,480
So,

536
00:29:48,040 --> 00:29:49,880
I don't want to call you uncle anymore.

537
00:29:49,880 --> 00:29:50,480
I want to

538
00:29:50,880 --> 00:29:52,080
call you by your name,

539
00:29:52,600 --> 00:29:53,840
Gu Jingyuan.

540
00:29:57,320 --> 00:30:00,320
