549
00:30:22,880 --> 00:30:24,320
to get the wrong idea.

550
00:30:35,280 --> 00:30:35,960
Uncle,

551
00:30:36,560 --> 00:30:37,160
why are you

552
00:30:37,480 --> 00:30:38,560
so old-fashioned?

553
00:30:39,160 --> 00:30:40,760
I don't want you to misunderstand.

554
00:30:40,760 --> 00:30:42,690
That's why I didn't explain to you.

555
00:30:44,160 --> 00:30:44,920
I've been

556
00:30:45,680 --> 00:30:46,640
