557
00:30:47,080 --> 00:30:48,120
abroad.

558
00:30:48,480 --> 00:30:49,740
I'm used to being free.

559
00:30:49,960 --> 00:30:50,720
I just think

560
00:30:51,080 --> 00:30:52,410
we're about the same age

561
00:30:52,840 --> 00:30:54,300
and we get along very well.

562
00:30:54,480 --> 00:30:54,880
So

563
00:30:55,280 --> 00:30:57,140
I don't want to see you as my elder.

564
00:30:58,360 --> 00:30:59,360
I want to treat you

565
00:31:00,160 --> 00:31:01,280
as my best friend.

566
00:31:05,800 --> 00:31:07,200
In our town,

567
00:31:07,480 --> 00:31:08,720
best friends would

568
00:31:08,920 --> 00:31:11,160
kiss each other's cheeks.

569
00:31:12,640 --> 00:31:13,280
Like this.

570
00:31:17,400 --> 00:31:18,240
That's all.

571
00:31:20,800 --> 00:31:21,260
Really?

572
00:31:22,240 --> 00:31:23,400
If you don't believe me,

573
00:31:23,400 --> 00:31:25,040
