576
00:31:42,720 --> 00:31:43,250
about it.

577
00:31:46,240 --> 00:31:46,970
Cheapskate.

578
00:31:48,360 --> 00:31:49,560
I'm done explaining.

579
00:31:49,880 --> 00:31:50,600
I'm going back.
